features: 【WELL STRUCTURED】This small gym bag can keep its shape even when it is empty. It's has a detachable shoulder strap, can be carried on shoulder or crossbody by adjusting different lengths. With padded top handles to keep your hands from being hurting.
【THREE POCKETS COMPARTEMNT】The overnight bag has 1 main compartment with 2 zippered pockets, it can keep your things individually.
【FUNCTIONAL WEEKENDER BAG】This is a lockable carry on weekender bag, easy organization 1-3 days luggage. Perfect to fit under the plane seat when travel as a personal item bag.
【LIGHTWEIGHT SPORT HOLDALL BAG】The sport holdall bag fits perfectly for gym stuff, easy to put in to lockers. 18" size can hold workout clothes, a pair of shoe, jump rope, water bottle, toiletries.
【MORE THAN OCCASIONS FOR USE】More than 20 scenarios for use, our small duffel bag does it all. Basketball training bag, cheerleading bag, gymnastic team bag, emergency bag ect.
